-- Video Doesn't Change China's Position on Trawler Collision, Xinhua Reports
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-11-05T14:55:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-05/video-doesn-t-change-china-s-position-on-trawler-collision-xinhua-reports.html
China has reiterated its position
that the video showing the collision of a Chinese trawler with
Japanese patrol boats doesn’t undermine its assertion of the
illegality of Japan’s actions, Xinhua News Agency said, citing a
statement rom Hong Lei, a Foreign Ministry spokesman.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
